                    (b) the adjacent area for the Territory of Ashmore and Cartier Islands, within the meaning of section 5A(3) of the Petroleum Submerged Lands Act, other than the territorial sea within that area; and
                    (c) the space above and below the areas described in paragraphs (a) and (b).
            (5) The adjacent area for a State or the Northern Territory does not include any area inside the limits of a State or Territory.
